rows.label: qst201510_0010
rows.name: A loose end? Just who do you think I am, sweetie?

rows.label: qst201510_0020
rows.name:
Wait, you know where they're
taking the Thanatitan?

rows.label: qst201510_0030
rows.name:
I'm hurt. It seems you were really doubting
I could get the job done. It breaks my heart.

rows.label: qst201510_0040
rows.name: No no, we weren't really doubting you...

rows.label: qst201510_0050
rows.name: Hahaha... Just teasing.

rows.label: qst201510_0060
rows.name:
I'm always willing to go the extra mile
for my darling Driver...

rows.label: qst201510_0070
rows.name: Ah. She can use her Clairvoyant Eye.

rows.label: qst201510_0080
rows.name: Just give me a moment.

rows.label: qst201510_0090
rows.name: How was it? Did you see anything?

rows.label: qst201510_0100
rows.name:
There was some sort of giant ether mine,
and men doing some sort of work.

rows.label: qst201510_0110
rows.name:
And there was a large contraption.
I'd never seen one like it before...

rows.label: qst201510_0120
rows.name:
The Thanatitan was right next to it.
I saw Gulan men too, a stone's throw away.

rows.label: qst201510_0130
rows.name: An ether mine?

rows.label: qst201510_0140
rows.name: Is there even place like that in Invidia?

rows.label: qst201510_0150
rows.name: It was in Superbia.

rows.label: qst201510_0160
rows.name: You can see that far?!

rows.label: qst201510_0170
rows.name: Haha. Of course.

rows.label: qst201510_0180
rows.name: With my eye, no matter how far apart we may be...

rows.label: qst201510_0190
rows.name:
I can watch my sweetie-pie Driver,
wherever they are, and whenever I like.

rows.label: qst201510_0200
rows.name: Gross.

rows.label: qst201510_0210
rows.name:
Ahem - we're looking for an Superbian
ether mine, you say.

rows.label: qst201510_0220
rows.name: Exactly.

rows.label: qst201510_0230
rows.name: I wonder what the contraption could be?

rows.label: qst201510_0240
rows.name: Must be big thing, like Sakura!

rows.label: qst201510_0250
rows.name:
But...if that's true, then where does the
Thanatitan come into all this?

rows.label: qst201510_0260
rows.name:
If we assume that they're to be using
the Thanatitan in the ether mine...

rows.label: qst201510_0270
rows.name: Then, contraption used to carry Thanatitan...?

rows.label: qst201510_0280
rows.name:
The flow of ether acts much like our own blood,
in that it circulates around the Divine Beasts' bodies.

rows.label: qst201510_0290
rows.name:
If they use the Thanatitan there, they'll be able to
accelerate the Mor Superbian Divine Beast's degradation!

rows.label: qst201510_0300
rows.name: Then we've no time to lose!

rows.label: qst201510_0310
rows.name:
If they get away with their scheme, Superbia's
gonna be in big trouble!

rows.label: qst201510_0320
rows.name:
Agreed. Let's make haste to Superbia
and apprehend the culprits at once!

rows.label: qst201510_0330
rows.name: Hahaha... I do enjoy the thrill of the chase!
